    {
      "_id": "k8xZPap3K3F3YKpP",
      "name": "The Dog That Never Blinks",
      "type": "ability",
      "img": "icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-teal.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>Observant PCs may notice Dreyfus's tells: he never blinks, he watches mouths more than hands, he does not eat (his bowl has been full for days), he does not sleep, and his ears flatten in <em>attention</em>&mdash;not fear&mdash;when he hears the word 'Kaelen.' A Hard Intuition test reveals that something is deeply wrong with this animal.</p>",
        "reference": "",
        "novice": {
          "isActive": true,
          "action": "A",
          "description": "<p>Observant PCs may notice Dreyfus's tells: he never blinks, he watches mouths more than hands, he does not eat (his bowl has been full for days), he does not sleep, and his ears flatten in <em>attention</em>&mdash;not fear&mdash;when he hears the word 'Kaelen.' A Hard Intuition test reveals that something is deeply wrong with this animal.</p>"
